    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparatuses used to slice cheese, typically comprising a board and an attached knife or wire for cutting the cheese. One example comprises a guillotine-style metal blade equipped with a wooden handle attached to a wooden turnstyle cutting block.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
